# React Trainers App

## Description

This project demonstrates React Router by implementing navigation between multiple pages and displaying trainer details using dynamic routes and URL parameters.

## Technologies Used

- React
- React Router DOM
- JavaScript (ES6)
- HTML
- CSS
- Node.js
- npm

## Features

- React Router
- Navigation Menu
- Dynamic Routing
- URL Parameter Passing
- Trainer List
- Trainer Details Page

## Project Structure

```
trainersapp
│
├── src
│   ├── Components
│   │   ├── Home.js
│   │   ├── TrainersList.js
│   │   └── TrainerDetails.js
│   ├── trainer.js
│   ├── TrainersMock.js
│   ├── App.js
│   └── index.js
```

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/trainersapp.git
cd trainersapp
npm install
npm install react-router-dom
npm start
```

## Learning Outcomes

- React Router DOM
- BrowserRouter
- Routes and Route
- Link Component
- Dynamic Routing
- URL Parameters using useParams()
- Navigation between Components
